
==============================================================================
==============================================================================
=================== [ Ionis Users Informations PHP Class ] ===================
==============================================================================

A PHP Class to get informations about students in Ionis group :
Isbp, Epitech, Etna, Ipsa, Epita, e-art, Web@cademie, ...

================================= [ News! ] ==================================

2012-02-17: The basic version is no longer maintained! It was too slow...
	    Please use the SQL version from now.

============================== [ Requirement ] ===============================

- PHP >= 5.3
- libssh2-php
- MySQL (mysql-server, php5-mysql)

================================= [ Usage ] ==================================

1) Initialisation

   $iui = new IonisInfo($mysql_login, $mysql_pass, $database_name,
			$iui_login, $iui_unix_pass);

   Optional parameter : $path_local_files (string)

2) Functions

- Check if a login exist
    $iui->isLogin($login);

- Get a login from the uid :
    $iui->getLoginFromUid($uid)

- Get uid, name, group, school, promo, city from the login :
    $iui->getUid($login);
    $iui->getName($login); // Optional parameter $uppercase (bool)
    $iui->getGroup($login);
    $iui->getSchool($login); // Optional parameter $uppercase (bool)
    $iui->getPromo($login);
    $iui->getCity($login);

- Get all informations from the login in an array :
    $iui->getUserByLogin($login);

- Get Report Url :
    $iui->getReportUrl($login);

- Get photos :
    $iui->getPhotoUrl($login);
    get the url from the intra.
    $iui->copyPhoto($login, $directory);
    copy the photo locally.

- Get .plan file :
    $iui->getPlan($plan);
    copy the .plan public file (afs) locally and return its content.

- Check the PPP password :
    $iui->checkPass($login, $pass);
    return true if the password match for the login, false otherwise.

- Update informations files
    $iui->updateFiles();
    update the informations files. Good idea to put it in a crontab.

- Get MySQL table Id

   - Get login from the id :
     $iui->getLoginFromId($id)

   - Get the id from the login :
     $iui->getId($login);


3) Example

   See the example.php file.

